\c 13
\s Abhuramu naRoti vanoparadzana
\p
\v 1 Zvino Abhuramu wakakwira, akabva Ijipiti, iye nomukadzi wake, nezvose zvaakanga anazvo, naRo­tiwo anaye; vakaenda kurutivi rwenyasi.
\v 2 Abhuramu wakanga akapfuma kwazvo mombe, nesirivha, nendarama.
\v 3 Akafa­mba nzendo dzake achibva nyasi kusvi­kira paBheteri, kunzvimbo iya kwaiva netende rake pakutanga, pakati peBheteri neAi;
\v 4 kunzvimbo yeatari, yaakanga ai­tapo pakutanga; Abhuramu akanamata zita raJehovha ipapo.
\p
\v 5 NaRoti, iye wakaenda naAbhu­ramu, wakanga aine makwai, nemombe, namatende.
\v 6 Nyika ikasavaringana, kuti vagare panzvimbo imwe; nokuti pfuma yavo yakanga iri zhinji; vakasagona ku­gara panzvimbo imwe.
\v 7 Vafudzi vezvi­pfuwo zvaAbhuramu navafudzi vezvi­pfuwo zvaRoti vakaita nharo; vaKenani navaPerezi vakanga vagere panyika iyo.
\p
\v 8 Ipapo Abhuramu akati kuna Roti, "Nharo ngadzirege kuvapo pakati pangu newe, napakati pavafudzi vangu navafu­dzi vako, nokuti tiri hama.
\v 9 Ko nyika yose haizi pamberi pako here? Para­dzana hako neni; kana iwe ukaenda kuruboshwe, ini ndichaenda kurudyi; kana iwe ukaenda kurudyi ini ndichae­nda kuruboshwe."
\p
\v 10 Roti akasimudzira meso ake, akaona bani rose reJorodhani, kuti raka­nga riine mvura pose, Jehovha achigere kuparadza Sodhomu neGomora; rakanga rakaita somunda waJehovha, senyika yeIjipiti, kana munhu achienda Zoari.
\v 11 Roti akazvitsaurira bani rose reJorodhani; Roti akaenda kurutivi rwamabvazuva; vakapa­radzana havo.
\v 12 Abhuramu akagara pa­nyika yeKenani, Roti akagara pamaguta aiva kubani, akaswededzera tende rake kusvikira paSodhomu.
\v 13 Zvino varume veSodhomu vakanga vakaipa, vaitadzira Jehovha kwazvo-kwazvo.
\p
\v 14 Zvino Roti wakati aparadzana naye, Jehovha akati kuna Abhuramu, "Simudza hako meso ako ipapo paugere, utarire kurutivi rwokumusoro, norwe­nyasi, norwokumabvazuva, norwokuma­virira;
\v 15 nokuti nyika yose yaunoona, ndichaipa iwe navana vako nokusinga­peri.
\v 16 Ndichaita vana vako seguruva renyika; kuti kana kuine munhu anogona kuverenga guruva renyika, navana vako vangaverengwawo.
\v 17 Simuka, ufambe nenyika pakureba kwayo, napaupamhi hwayo, nokuti ndichakupa iyo."
\v 18 Ipapo Abhuramu wakabvisa tende rake, aka­ndogara pamiti yemiouki yeMamure, iri paHebhuroni, akavakirapo Jehovha atari.
